Package: FAIRML
Title: Fairness-aware machine learning methods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Indre", "Zliobaite", email = "zliobaite@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Methods for measuring discrimination in data, measuring discrimination due to  algorithms (decision rules), and sanitizing algorithms such that decisions supported by model predictions (e.g. interest rates for loans) are not discriminatory with respect to externally given protected characteristics (e.g. age, race, gender).
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
